high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter near the toaster.
Pick up the knife that is right of the toaster.
Turn right, move to the counter near the bread.
Slice the lettuce with the knife.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife on to the lowest shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn right, move to the counter near the bread.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left, move to in front of the sink.
Place the slice of lettuce into the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the slice of lettuce on to the lowest shelf in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Slice lettuce, rinse it, put it into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the counter in front of you
Pick up the knife that is sitting on the counter
Take a step to your right.
Slice the lettuce with the knife
Turn left and walk to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the knife on the bottom shelf then close the fridge
Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the toaster
Pick up a slice of lettuce
Turn left and walk to the sink that is across the room
Place the slice of lettuce in the sink and turn on the faucet.  Turn off the faucet and pick up the slice of lettuce
Turn around and walk to the black fridge
Open the fridge and place the lettuce on the bottom shelf behind the knife and then close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Place clean lettuce into a fridge

high_descs: Turn left, go straight and to the left to the counter with the knife.
Take the knife from the counter.
Move right to face the lettuce.
Cut the on the counter lettuce into slices.
Turn left, go straight, turn left, go straight, turn right at the fridge, go straight to the fridge.
Put the knife on the lowest shelf of the fridge in the center near the edge.
Turn right, go straight, turn right, turn left to the lettuce on the counter, go to the counter.
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn left, go straight, turn left, go straight and slightly left to the counter to the right of the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink. Take the lettuce from the sink.
Turn right, go straight past the counter's end on the right, turn right, go straight then turn left at the fridge. Go to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the lowest shelf of the fridge behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of lettuce in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the left and approach the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Step to the right to face the vegetable on the counter.
Cut the vegetable on the counter into slices.
Turn left and walk around the room to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge to the right of the tomato.
Turn to the right, walk around the corner and turn left to face the vegetable on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the vegetable on the counter.
Turn right and walk around the kitchen to the sink and face it.
Place the piece of vegetable in the sink, wash it, remove it.
Turn around and walk forward, then face the fridge on the left.
Place the piece of vegetable in the fridge next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: To cut a vegetable as well as put it plus a knife into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the left and approach the counter with a green vegetable on it.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to face the vegetable on the counter.
Cut the vegetable on the counter into slices.
Turn to the left and walk around to face to fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge next to the tomato.
Turn right and walk back to face the counter with the sliced vegetable on it.
Pick up a slice of the vegetable on the counter.
Walk to the opposite side of the room and face the sink.
Put the slice of vegetable in the sink, wash it off, pick it back up.
Turn to the right, walk across the room to face the fridge.
Put the slice of vegetable in the fridge above the knife.
anns.task_desc: To cut a vegetable into slices, wash a slice, store it in the fridge with the knife.
